  ID: 631057a1-0221-4885-ba61-78b661b62b70
  Source:
    Title: The Book of Hours
    Locus: I 13
  Locus:
    Daily: December 2
Format: Verse
Title: In Your Sight
---
I want to unfold.
Let no place in me hold itself closed,
for when I am closed, I am false.
I want to stay clear in your sight.
